{"type":"message","id":"da9a3017","parentId":"4af53c67","timestamp":"2026-03-18T12:19:31.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我了解了任务配置：\n\n从 `fanqie-accounts.js` 配置：\n- 有2个账号（主账号和小号）\n- 主账号有3部作品（都是已签约）：\n  1. 枪与凋零之花\n  2. 咳血少女与前世宿敌的百合维新\n  3. 无纪年王国\n- 小号暂时没有作品\n- 每部作品每天发布2章\n- 章节间隔10分钟\n- 作品间隔30分钟\n- 账号间隔60分钟\n\n预计发布任务：\n- 主账号：3作品 × 2章 = 6章\n- 小号：0作品 = 0章\n- 总计：6章\n\n现在让我检查 `publish-to-fanqie.js` 是否存在，以及今天的发布状态：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d00e304311e1acd732761f2f61a91","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /workspace/projects/auto-scripts/task-planner/scripts/publish-to-fanqie.js"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d00e30583fd96bf5e9ea9716cf236","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/auto-scripts/task-planner/scripts/publish-to-fanqie.js","limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":807,"output":422,"cacheRead":24128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25357,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773836367734}}
